{"title":"Fx Hueso patológico","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Ortogeriatría/Orto Fx Hueso patológico-2026.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Fractura de Hueso\\NPatológico","guid":"ybOI7R7DhUGS5JfgtF_HEQ","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Definiciones","guid":"","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"**Fractura Patológica** → fractura a través\\Nde hueso debilitado por patología","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"**Fractura Inminente** →\\Ndestrucción ósea con riesgo\\Ninminente, continuidad aún presente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"**Evento Relacionado al Esqueleto\\N(ERE)** → fractura, dolor,\\Nhipercalcemia, compresión medular","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"5","parent":"0","text":"Etiología","guid":"","children":[{"id":"6","parent":"5","text":"Causas tumorales (más frecuentes)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"7","parent":"6","text":"Metástasis óseas (~80% de mama,\\Npróstata, pulmón, tiroides, riñón)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"6","text":"**Mieloma Múltiple** → tasas más altas\\Npor patrón puramente lítico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"6","text":"Tumores primarios óseos (sarcomas)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"10","parent":"5","text":"Causas no tumorales","guid":"","children":[{"id":"11","parent":"10","text":"Condiciones metabólicas\\N(osteoporosis severa)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"10","text":"Infecciones (osteomielitis)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"10","text":"Osteonecrosis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"10","text":"Iatrogenia → corticoides,\\Nbifosfonatos (fracturas atípicas)","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"15","parent":"0","text":"Epidemiología","guid":"","children":[{"id":"16","parent":"15","text":"Incidencia en pacientes con\\Nmetástasis óseas → **5-29%**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"15","text":"Sitios más frecuentes\\Nen huesos largos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"18","parent":"17","text":"**Fémur** → más común","guid":"","children":[{"id":"19","parent":"18","text":"Cuello femoral **50%**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"18","text":"Subtrocantérica **30%**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"18","text":"Intertrocantérica **20%**","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"22","parent":"17","text":"Tibia → segundo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"17","text":"Húmero → tercero","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"24","parent":"0","text":"Patrón Óseo según Tumor","guid":"","children":[{"id":"25","parent":"24","text":"**Puramente Lítico**","guid":"","children":[{"id":"26","parent":"25","text":"Mieloma Múltiple","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"25","text":"Carcinoma Renal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"25","text":"Carcinoma Tiroides","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"29","parent":"24","text":"Lítico o Mixto","guid":"","children":[{"id":"30","parent":"29","text":"Cáncer de Pulmón","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"29","text":"Cáncer de Mama","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"32","parent":"24","text":"**Predominantemente Osteoblástico**","guid":"","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"Cáncer de Próstata","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"34","parent":"0","text":"Presentación Clínica","guid":"","children":[{"id":"35","parent":"34","text":"Mecanismo → trauma de\\N**baja energía** (mínimo)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"34","text":"Síntomas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"37","parent":"36","text":"**Dolor** → más común,\\Nprecede a la fractura","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"36","text":"Equimosis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"36","text":"Masa de tejido blando →\\Nextensión tumoral extraósea","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"36","text":"Incapacidad de carga\\N(extremidad inferior)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"36","text":"Síntomas neurológicos →\\Nfracturas vertebrales","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"42","parent":"34","text":"Diferenciación del dolor","guid":"","children":[{"id":"43","parent":"42","text":"**Dolor Biológico** →\\Nnocturno/matutino, resuelve durante\\Nel día → NO indica fractura inminente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"42","text":"**Dolor Mecánico** → persistente,\\N**empeora con carga** → indica\\Ninestabilidad/fractura","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"45","parent":"0","text":"Evaluación Diagnóstica","guid":"","children":[{"id":"46","parent":"45","text":"Objetivos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"47","parent":"46","text":"Delinear extensión ósea\\Ny partes blandas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"46","text":"Determinar compromiso\\Nesquelético total","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"46","text":"**Diagnóstico histológico**\\N(obligatorio si lesión única)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"46","text":"Estimar pronóstico","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"51","parent":"45","text":"Imágenes","guid":"","children":[{"id":"52","parent":"51","text":"Radiografía Simple → prueba inicial","guid":"","children":[{"id":"53","parent":"52","text":"Lesiones líticas\\N(lucentes, permeativas)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"52","text":"Lesiones blásticas (escleróticas)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"52","text":"Reacción perióstica (Triángulo\\NCodman, Sol naciente)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"52","text":"Limitación → ~**10%**\\Nfalsos negativos","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"57","parent":"51","text":"TC → anatomía compleja,\\Nintegridad cortical","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"51","text":"**RM con Gadolinio** → Gold Standard\\Npara metástasis espinales","guid":"","children":[{"id":"59","parent":"58","text":"Fractura maligna → señal T1 baja\\Nbien definida, masa tejido blando,\\Ncompromiso pedículos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"58","text":"Fractura insuficiencia → edema difuso, sin\\Nmasa, sin compromiso posterior","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"61","parent":"51","text":"PET/TC","guid":"","children":[{"id":"62","parent":"61","text":"**SUVmax >3-4** → altamente\\Nespecífico para malignidad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"61","text":"**SUVmax <3** →\\Nsugiere benignidad","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"64","parent":"45","text":"Biopsia","guid":"","children":[{"id":"65","parent":"64","text":"**REGLA** → lesión solitaria = NUNCA\\Nfijar sin diagnóstico tisular","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"64","text":"Riesgo → si es sarcoma primario,\\Nfijación contamina compartimento","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"64","text":"Excepción → múltiples lesiones con\\Ndiagnóstico histológico previo","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"68","parent":"0","text":"Evaluación de Riesgo de Fractura","guid":"","children":[{"id":"69","parent":"68","text":"**Score de Mirels** (huesos largos)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"70","parent":"69","text":"Variables (1-3 puntos c/u)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"71","parent":"70","text":"Sitio → superior (1) / inferior (2) /\\N**peritrocantérico (3)**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"70","text":"Dolor → leve (1) / moderado (2) /\\N**funcional/mecánico (3)**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"70","text":"Lesión → blástica (1) /\\Nmixta (2) / **lítica (3)**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"70","text":"Tamaño → <1/3 (1) / 1/3-2/3 (2)\\N/ **>2/3 diámetro (3)**","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"75","parent":"69","text":"Interpretación","guid":"","children":[{"id":"76","parent":"75","text":"≤7 → riesgo bajo → observación/RT","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"75","text":"8 → intermedio → individualizar","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"75","text":"**≥9 → riesgo alto (33% fractura)** →\\Nestabilización profiláctica","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"79","parent":"69","text":"Limitación → sensibilidad >90%,\\N**especificidad solo 13%** (sobretrata)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"80","parent":"68","text":"Análisis Rigidez Estructural (CTRA)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"81","parent":"80","text":"Sensibilidad 100%, Especificidad\\N61% → mejor que Mirels","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"82","parent":"68","text":"Criterios de Riesgo Cortical","guid":"","children":[{"id":"83","parent":"82","text":"Destrucción axial **>30 mm**\\N→ riesgo fractura 25%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"82","text":"Destrucción circunferencial\\N**>50%** → predictor de fractura","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"85","parent":"68","text":"**SINS (Score Inestabilidad\\NEspinal Neoplásica)**","guid":"","children":[{"id":"86","parent":"85","text":"0-6 → estable","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"85","text":"**7-12 → potencialmente\\Ninestable** → consulta quirúrgica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"85","text":"13-18 → inestable → cirugía","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"89","parent":"0","text":"Principios de Manejo Quirúrgico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"90","parent":"89","text":"Objetivo → paliación que dure toda\\Nla supervivencia esperada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"89","text":"**Regla crítica** → fijación NO debe\\Ndepender de consolidación ósea","guid":"","children":[{"id":"92","parent":"91","text":"Ca Pulmón → **0% unión ósea**\\Ncon manejo conservador","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"93","parent":"89","text":"Contraindicaciones","guid":"","children":[{"id":"94","parent":"93","text":"Paciente moribundo\\N(supervivencia < tiempo\\Nrecuperación)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"93","text":"Estado funcional muy pobre\\Nsin mejoría esperable","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"96","parent":"89","text":"Tiempos de recuperación","guid":"","children":[{"id":"97","parent":"96","text":"Clavo/Placa/Hemiartroplastia\\N→ **≤6 semanas**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"96","text":"Reconstrucciones complejas\\N(acetábulo) → **3-6 meses**","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"99","parent":"89","text":"Opciones de Fijación","guid":"","children":[{"id":"100","parent":"99","text":"**Clavo Intramedular** → estándar para\\Ndiáfisis (fémur, tibia, húmero)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"101","parent":"100","text":"Permite carga inmediata","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"102","parent":"99","text":"Reconstrucción Endoprotésica →\\Ndestrucción yuxtaarticular","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"103","parent":"99","text":"Placa/Tornillos →\\Nalternativa húmero distal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"99","text":"**Relleno con Cemento (PMMA)**\\N→ estabilidad inmediata","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"105","parent":"89","text":"Controversias resueltas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"106","parent":"105","text":"Vástago largo → NO rutinario\\N(riesgo embolia **12.5%**)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"105","text":"**Cemento vs Press-fit** → cemento es\\Nestándar (menor aflojamiento)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"108","parent":"105","text":"Cuello femoral → **artroplastia, NO\\Ntornillos** (alta tasa de falla)","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"109","parent":"0","text":"Radioterapia","guid":"","children":[{"id":"110","parent":"109","text":"RT Postoperatoria","guid":"","children":[{"id":"111","parent":"110","text":"**Recomendación Grado 2C** →\\Nmayoría de tumores sólidos/linfoma","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"112","parent":"110","text":"Beneficios → remineralización, alivio\\Ndolor, reduce fallo implante","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"113","parent":"110","text":"Esquemas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"114","parent":"113","text":"**Preferido** → 20 Gy\\Nen 5 fracciones","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"113","text":"Alternativa → 30 Gy en 10 fracciones","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"116","parent":"113","text":"8 Gy dosis única → NO\\Nrecomendada postoperatorio","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"117","parent":"110","text":"Inicio → 2-4 semanas post-cirugía","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"118","parent":"109","text":"RT como Alternativa a Cirugía","guid":"","children":[{"id":"119","parent":"118","text":"Tumores radiosensibles\\N(Mieloma, Linfoma, Ca Mama)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"120","parent":"118","text":"81% fracturas inminentes femorales con\\NRT → no requirieron cirugía","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"121","parent":"0","text":"Manejo Farmacológico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"122","parent":"121","text":"Inhibidores de Osteoclastos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"123","parent":"122","text":"Bifosfonatos (Ácido Zoledrónico)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"122","text":"**Denosumab**","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"125","parent":"121","text":"Eficacia → reducen ERE **25-40%**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"126","parent":"121","text":"**Denosumab vs\\NZoledrónico** (metaanálisis\\N2025)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"127","parent":"126","text":"Denosumab superior en retrasar ERE","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"126","text":"Denosumab ↓ fracturas\\Npatológicas en Ca Mama **39%**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"129","parent":"126","text":"Excepción → Mieloma\\NMúltiple (sin diferencia)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"126","text":"Riesgos Denosumab → mayor\\Nhipocalcemia, osteonecrosis mandibular","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"131","parent":"121","text":"Función → complementario, **NO\\Nsustituye cirugía ni RT**","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"132","parent":"0","text":"Sitios Específicos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"133","parent":"132","text":"Columna Vertebral","guid":"","children":[{"id":"134","parent":"133","text":"Decisión NOMS → Neurológico,\\NOncológico, Mecánico, Sistémico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"133","text":"Indicaciones quirúrgicas → inestabilidad\\N(SINS alto), compresión medular","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"133","text":"Aumento Vertebral","guid":"","children":[{"id":"137","parent":"136","text":"Cifoplastia → restaura altura,\\Nmás cara, menos fugas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"136","text":"Vertebroplastia → no\\Nrestaura altura, más barata","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"139","parent":"136","text":"**Contraindicación** →\\Ncolumna cervical, infección","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"140","parent":"132","text":"Pelvis/Acetábulo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"141","parent":"140","text":"Clasificación de Harrington (I-IV)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"140","text":"Tratamiento → ATC compleja\\N(anillos reforzamiento)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"140","text":"AORIF → técnica\\Nmínimamente invasiva para\\Nfrágiles","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"144","parent":"0","text":"Complicaciones","guid":"","children":[{"id":"145","parent":"144","text":"Tromboembolismo Venoso","guid":"","children":[{"id":"146","parent":"145","text":"Tasa global → **7.1%**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"145","text":"EP → 3.9%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"145","text":"TVP → 3.3%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"149","parent":"145","text":"**Profilaxis obligatoria**","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"150","parent":"0","text":"Consideraciones Geriátricas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"151","parent":"150","text":"Fragilidad → considerar en\\Ndecisión quirúrgica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"152","parent":"150","text":"Polifarmacia → interacciones con\\Nbifosfonatos, anticoagulantes","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"153","parent":"150","text":"Función basal → determina\\Ncandidatura a cirugía compleja","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"154","parent":"150","text":"Delirium → riesgo\\Nelevado postoperatorio","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"155","parent":"150","text":"Proporcionalidad → tiempo\\Nrecuperación vs supervivencia esperada","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"156","parent":"0","text":"Perlas Clínicas ⭐","guid":"","children":[{"id":"157","parent":"156","text":"Lesión solitaria = NUNCA fijar sin\\Nbiopsia previa (descartar sarcoma)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"158","parent":"156","text":"Mirels ≥9 = fijación profiláctica\\Nrecomendada (aunque sobreindica)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"159","parent":"156","text":"PET SUVmax >3-4 = altamente\\Nespecífico para malignidad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"160","parent":"156","text":"Dolor mecánico (con carga) = inestabilidad\\Nhasta demostrar lo contrario","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"156","text":"Gammagrafía falsamente\\Nnegativa en Mieloma y Ca Renal\\N(usar PET o serie ósea)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"156","text":"Fijación debe soportar carga de por vida\\NSIN depender de consolidación","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"163","parent":"156","text":"Cemento SIEMPRE en artroplastias\\Nmetastásicas (estabilidad inmediata)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"164","parent":"156","text":"Cuello femoral patológico =\\Nartroplastia, NUNCA tornillos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"165","parent":"156","text":"Profilaxis > tratamiento de fractura\\Nestablecida (menor morbilidad)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"166","parent":"156","text":"Columna cervical =\\Ncifoplastia/vertebroplastia\\NCONTRAINDICADAS","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"167","parent":"156","text":"Ca Pulmón = peor pronóstico, 0%\\Nconsolidación con manejo conservador","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"156","text":"Denosumab preferido en Ca\\NMama por ↓ fracturas 39%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"169","parent":"156","text":"Mieloma = patrón puramente\\Nlítico, muy radiosensible","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":176,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Geriatría","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Ortogeriatría","filename":"Orto Fx Hueso patológico-2026","id":"map_1532","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"Orto Fx Hueso patológico-2026"}